%N A167649 Number of reduced words of length n in Coxeter group on 4 generators S_i with relations (S_i)^2 = (S_i S_j)^15 = I.
%C A167649 The initial terms coincide with those of A003946, although the two sequences are eventually different.
%C A167649 Computed with Magma using commands similar to those used to compute A154638.
%H A167649 G. C. Greubel, <a href="/A167649/b167649.txt">Table of n, a(n) for n = 0..500</a>
%H A167649 <a href="/index/Rec#order_15">Index entries for linear recurrences with constant coefficients</a>, signature (2, 2, 2, 2, 2, 2, 2, 2, 2, 2, 2, 2, 2, 2, -3).
%F A167649 G.f.: (t^15 + 2*t^14 + 2*t^13 + 2*t^12 + 2*t^11 + 2*t^10 + 2*t^9 + 2*t^8 + 2*t^7 + 2*t^6 + 2*t^5 + 2*t^4 + 2*t^3 + 2*t^2 + 2*t + 1)/(3*t^15 - 2*t^14 - 2*t^13 - 2*t^12 - 2*t^11 - 2*t^10 - 2*t^9 - 2*t^8 - 2*t^7 - 2*t^6 - 2*t^5 - 2*t^4 - 2*t^3 - 2*t^2 - 2*t + 1).
%t A167649 CoefficientList[Series[(t^15 + 2*t^14 + 2*t^13 + 2*t^12 + 2*t^11 + 2*t^10 + 2*t^9 + 2*t^8 + 2*t^7 + 2*t^6 + 2*t^5 + 2*t^4 + 2*t^3 + 2*t^2 + 2*t + 1)/(3*t^15 - 2*t^14 - 2*t^13 - 2*t^12 - 2*t^11 - 2*t^10 - 2*t^9 - 2*t^8 - 2*t^7 - 2*t^6 - 2*t^5 - 2*t^4 - 2*t^3 - 2*t^2 - 2*t + 1), {t, 0, 50}], t] (* _G. C. Greubel_, Jun 18 2016 *)
%o A167649 (PARI) first(n)=Vec((1+x^5+x^10)*(1+x+x^2+x^3+x^4)*(1+x)/(1-2*x-2*x^2-2*x^3-2*x^4-2*x^5-2*x^6-2*x^7-2*x^8-2*x^9-2*x^10-2*x^11-2*x^12-2*x^13-2*x^14+3*x^15)+O(x^(n+1))) \\ _Charles R Greathouse IV_, Jun 12 2026
